	<text xml:lang="la">
		<body>
			<div>
				<p>
					<s n="1" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Dominus Iesus Christus, unicus servator noster, benedicat tibi, princeps illustrissime et domine clementissime, et servet te tuosque ab omni malo!</s>
					<s n="2" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Spero literas nostras generoso viro d. <persName type="auto_name">Belovacensi</persName> creditas iam tibi esse redditas.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="3" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Interea 10. iulii venit huc nobilissimus d. <persName type="citizen_name">a Montaigü</persName>, eques ordinis, qui inter alia petebat, ut, si aliquid de <persName type="auto_name" ref="p3753">rege Polonorum</persName> acciperem, mature tibi, principi meo perpetua observantia colendo, significarem.</s>
					<s n="4" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Ac potui hoc commode per hunc civem nostrum, qui ad te, domine clementissime, profecturus erat, perficere.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="5" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Ergo tertia abhinc die recta <persName type="auto_name">Patavio</persName> veniunt studiosi nobiles, viri certe egregii, duo <placeName type="auto_name">Rigenses</placeName> ex <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l2574" cert="high">Livonia</placeName>, tertius <persName type="citizen_name">Holsatus</persName> ex <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l825" cert="high">Dania</placeName>, redituri in patriam.</s>
					<s n="6" xml:lang="la" type="auto" ana="salute">Qui cum salutandi gratia me convenissent et a me rogarentur, indicarunt <persName type="auto_name" ref="p3753">regem Polonorum</persName> 11. iulii <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l522">Venetiis</placeName> expectari.</s>
					<s n="7" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Eo advenisse ducem <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l150">Ferrariensem</placeName>, qui ipsum <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l306" cert="high">Mediolanum</placeName> usque comitetur, unde mox per <persName type="auto_name">Taurinum</persName> festinet in <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l832" cert="high">Galliam</placeName>; deductum vero esse ab <persName type="citizen_name">imperatore Maximiliano</persName> <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l546" cert="high">Vienna</placeName> <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l850" cert="high">Austriae</placeName> Venetias usque.</s>
					<s n="8" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Addebant regem delusis <persName type="auto_name">Polonis</persName> celeribus equis <placeName ref="l546" cert="high">Viennam</placeName> evasisse.</s>
					<s n="9" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Caeterum haec ea fide, qua isti narrarunt mihi, tibi domino clementissimo narro.</s>
					<s n="10" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Heri vero duces militum nonnulli Helvetici hac transierunt <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l760">Salodurum</placeName> ad <placeName type="auto_name">Bellevreium</placeName>, regium legatum, pecunias, ut ferunt, accepturi, quibus militem conducant, quem intra paucos dies, ad 6000, in <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l832">Galliam</placeName> abducant regi.</s>
					<s n="11" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Mature vero amplissimae reipublicae nostrae magistratus ad omnes <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l862" cert="high">Helvet[iorum]</placeName> ordines eam misit supplicationem, quam mittendam praeterita septimana acceperat a d.  <persName type="auto_name">Montaigü</persName>, nec quod ego quidem sciam, quicquam adhuc responsi accepit.</s>
					<s n="12" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Qui vero has clementiae tuae affert, <persName type="auto_name">Georgius...</persName> blius, civis est nostrae urbis parentibus natus honestissimis; avus eius ordinis senatorii et quondam praefectus comitatus <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l21">Badensis</placeName> <placeName ref="l594" cert="high">Argoviae</placeName> in bello nostro <persName type="citizen_name">Capellano</persName>, quod respublica nostra gessit contra <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l2448" cert="high">5 Pagos</placeName>, una cum aliis viris piissimis fortiter occubuit.</s>
					<s n="13" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Ardet autem hic iuvenis singulari erga religionem veram ac erga te principem illustrissimum studio tibique, si commodum sit, inservire ac in aulam tuam recipi cupit.</s>
					<s n="14" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Hunc ergo clementiae, quam possum diligenter et studiose, commendo; iuvenis est integer, non degenerans a suis maioribus, ut sperem ipsum diligentem et fidelem futurum in omnibus.</s>
					<s n="15" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Si ulla re tibi, princeps illustrissime et domine clementissime inservire possum, me promptum exhibebo in omnibus.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="16" xml:lang="la" type="auto" ana="farewell">Vale, domine clementissime, una cum tuis omnibus.</s>
					<s n="17" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><placeName ref="l587" type="auto_name" cert="high">Tiguri</placeName> 18. iulii anno salutis nostrae 1574.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="18" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Clementiae tuae deditissimus <persName ref="p495" type="citizen_name" cert="high">Heinrychus Bullingerus</persName>, <placeName ref="l587" type="auto_name" cert="high">Tigurinae</placeName> ecclesiae minister etc.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="19" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Illustrissimo principi ac domino domino <persName type="citizen_name" cert="high" ref="p904">Heinrycho Borbonio</persName>, principi <placeName type="auto_name">Condensi</placeName>, domino suo clementissimo.</s>
				</p>
			</div>
